    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the potatoes are cooking, peel and slice 1/2<span class=\"text-danger\"> [1]</span> <strong>brown onion<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span></strong>finely and grate the <strong>remaining onion</strong></p><p>Peel and grate (don't chop!) the <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Combine the<strong> red wine paste</strong>,<strong> tomato paste </strong>and <strong>honey </strong>in a small bowl with 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp] </span><strong>cold water</strong> – this is your <strong>red wine glaze</strong></p>",
