    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>pork mince</strong> and <strong>grated onion</strong> in a medium bowl with the <strong>dried thyme</strong>, <strong>panko breadcrumbs</strong>, <strong>half</strong> the <strong>grated garlic</strong> and <strong>half</strong> the <strong>beef stock mix</strong></p><p>Season with a grind of <strong>pepper</strong> and using clean hands give everything a good mix up until fully combined – this is your <strong>pork mixture</strong></p><p>Shape the <strong>pork mixture</strong> into 2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[4] </span>mini<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>loaves</p><p>Reboil half a kettle</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1676975643463-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
