            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1676975648163-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, wash then chop the <strong>cavolo nero </strong>roughly, removing any tough stalks</p><p>Heat a separate, large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a very generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>drained potatoes </strong>with a generous pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and cook for 16-17 min or until golden and crispy, turning occasionally for even colouring</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1676975664681-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
