            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1676975673272-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>pork</strong> <strong>meatloaves</strong> with the <strong>crispy potatoes </strong>and<strong> Chantenay carrots & greens </strong>to the side</p><p>Add any <strong>remaining red wine glaze</strong> from the pan to the gravy and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>red wine gravy</strong></p><p>Drizzle the<strong> red wine gravy </strong>all over everything</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
